Author: AlexPechkin
Title: [BOUNTY| GoldMineCoin- Cryptocurrency provided by gold mining
Body: WEB |  Whitepaper | Telegram |  Youtube | Facebook    -About GMC- GMC- crypto-currency with the real weight of gold. We create a safe and stable crypto-currency secured by gold deposits in the Magadan Region of the Russian Federation, which will help you to save your funds at the time of the crisis, or to earn money by creating new gold deposits. In this way we create: • The mechanism for protecting the investment portfolio from the falls of the exchange rates • A means for long-term investments with high profitability (30 percent on the growth of the rate and increase in the stock of tokens due to the loyalty program from 10 to 1000 percent per year). • Tool for easy investment control, input of funds withdrawal in Cryptocurrency and back • This Token is equal to real gold. Thereby giving the possibility of exchange for real gold GMC coin weighing 1 to 5 ounce is protected by the blockchain technology, or for cash in accordance with the market price of gold, through the assignment of coins to the escrow company.  Main advantages of the project • The main guarantee is the operating from 2010 business with 13 tons of gold, 3,410 hectares (8400 acres) of land and machinery • Already invested 2.5 million dollars (Acquisition of the site, explosions at the site, clearance of the site, road construction, construction of the headquarters, installation and commissioning of ore processing equipment, etc.) • This is an option of obtaining a gold item (coin) weighing from 1 to 5 ounces. Each coin is protected by the QR code, which is in a blockchain. Either for cash in accordance with the market value of gold, by assigning coins to the Escrow company. • The bonus program for GMC members is 10 percent of the company’s profits to the participants of the bonus program, this gives (from $500,000 in the first year, and an increase in the size each year by several times) • Safety from the flop of the cryptocurrency at the exchange, by receiving the funds by Escrow Company at the rate of gold, by ceding the right to receive a coin • Stable growth of the GMC with the gold rate. Over the past 15 years, gold increased in price by 298.83% • Buy-back gmc tokens at the price of gold!  GMC club All buyers during an ICO of at least 1000 GMC can apply FOR FREE for membership in the club through a private office. The benefits of club membership: • The possibility of obtaining GMC coins from pure gold with anticounterfeiting protection on the blockchain. • Receiving additional bonus tokens - at a rate of 10 percent of the profit (for example, 10 members of the club own tokens in equal shares, twice a year they receive bonus tokens in the company of $ 1 million, with company profits of $ 10 million or $ 100 thousand for each member of the club). • Control over the process by voting via smart contracts. • The convenient input / output Fiat funds by assignment of tokens to the company or buying by bank card (after the introduction of the Easy Token system). • Obtaining full information about gold mining companies (accounting, the volume of mined ore) - opportunity to visit the mine by purchasing for a token tour package, with the possibility of independent gold mining. • Defending the interests of the club members..     Information on the token  The GoldMineCoin (GMC) token is developed according to the ERC20 standard, which is part of the Ethereum network, is compatible with wallets and exchanges. Our bounty program is divided into three parts: pre-sale, pre-ICO, ICO, - and according to this budget is divided into these time intervals in equal quantities.     The Bounty program includes a system of referral links. If specify in comments your wallet when buying a GMC, you get 0.5% of the purchase amount (wallets must be different). All communication of the bounty program is on the telegram channel: https://t.me/joinchat/DG3kkknPgOMG9P7y3QqXkg     All participants must subscribe to our social networks. Body: In order for us to fulfill the requirements of KYC. We need to know to whom to give out dividends (the information is closed). Become a member of the GMC club and get full information.  Club members receive non-public information about the balance sheet, the amount of mined gold, the dates of redemption and other insider data. The rest of the participants see only the online broadcast from the mine and the company news.
